Copyright:           (c) 2014 The University of Kansas
Category:            Web
Stability:           beta
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-version:       >= 1.10
Description:
  A transport-level remote JavaScript RESTful push mechanism.

data-files:
    static/js/kansas-comet.js

